# Trackmania Run History
[![Number of downloads](https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/json?color=fff&label=&query=downloads&suffix=%20downloads&url=https%3A%2F%2Fopenplanet.dev%2Fapi%2Fplugin%2F333&style=for-the-badge&logo=data:image/svg%2bxml;base64,)](https://openplanet.dev/plugin/333)
> Openplanet Plugin

Shows history of last N finishes in current session with delta to closest medal or pb. 


Requires [MLHook](https://openplanet.dev/plugin/mlhook) and [MLFeed](https://openplanet.dev/plugin/mlfeedracedata)

Supports [Champion Medal](https://openplanet.dev/plugin/championmedals)
